<br>
How many think this is unbalancing ? I played a level 29 druid as one of my alt, and already I can feel how powerful the dot is.  Death to mob while resting.  <br>
<br>
But given the snare and relative safety of the dot, don't you think it's too powerful ?  Given the fact that druid can snare and sow, this just makes them able to kill more powerful creatures even more easily ? - Just run around while they die is all druids need to do.<br>
<br>
Not trying to start a flamming argument here, I am just concerned this might be too big a boost for druids.  But since my druid is only level 29, I'd like to hear more opinions.<br>
<br>
Thanks. <br>
<br>
