If the mob was running away (feared or on its 'death march'), the DoT did full damage.<br>
If the mob was chasing you, the DoT did 66% damage.<br>
It was checked on a tick-by-tick basis.<br>
<br>
It was an anti-druid nerf. Other DoT users really weren't effected - Necro's normally fear their targets and Shaman either root them or melee them.<br>
<br>
